{"tid":557797,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"良品屋撚9年宵","createTime":"2018-02-11T16:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T17:26:47.000Z","uid":41564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6a245d833e353492f421cddfb46582dcbebd25b3","tid":557797,"uid":41564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"成班水魚搶住要抹布，所謂嘅勞作畫紙，之後話派刀具，又話有剃鬚刀，最後成班拎起曬d銀包要買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗 人真係好易俾人cap水，仲要cap易水都唔知，以為搶到平嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0ceb3e78d7b80cdebf519d876717b3a3031f50","tid":557797,"uid":42575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/135026_debd1257bbe40cf1abe6e6bee0801110.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F135026_debd1257bbe40cf1abe6e6bee0801110.png&h=964c8415&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家觀塘都有 有無巴打係附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe9611821d8a00de5aa7b0a1928afdf7edf32f6","tid":557797,"uid":285411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:26:47.000Z","msg":"大家小心，尋日呢班「良品屋」騙徒又喺深水埗鴨寮街開檔。<br />\n<br />\n又係用返嗰招，送完一大堆小禮物就開始示範個陶瓷煲，又係話送嘅不過要收返一千幾百表示誠意。我當時唔知係騙局，直到佢叫大家拎銀包出嚟我先扮冇錢走咗，結果我拎咗佢五塊抹布，四個掛勾同一塊玻璃鉆板。不過我見到有幾個阿叔阿嬸都有畀錢，有個仲好似畀得好唔情願咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n聽講呢間嘢除咗用「良品屋」呢個名之外，亦會用另一個名「28Home」出嚟呃人嘅。年近歲晚，大家小心唔好受騙！ <br />\n<br />\n個煲我冇買，上網搵個幅相係咁樣嘅：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYENmn0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYENmn0.jpg&h=01cf4907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我從騙徒身上攞到嘅「戰利品」：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBcy1pY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBcy1pY.jpg&h=b0fe00a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳媒報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27963746\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D27963746&d=cTbfhFij%2FhRN8MJ5IHlsRQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=04ac1aab\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27963746</a>"}]}